    "description": "SHARECARE https://www.sharecare.com\n\n\nFRONT-END ENGINEER\n\nDescription\n\nJoin our dynamic engineering team as a Front-End Engineer, where you'll thrive in a high-energy environment crafting products and features that directly influence people's lives. We are seeking a seasoned front-end engineer with expertise in developing responsive web and native applications using the React framework. If you're passionate about creating impactful user experiences and pushing the boundaries of technology, we want you on our team.\n\nRequirements\n\n - At least 3 years of practical experience in building web applications preferably in ReactJS or React Native\n\n - Must demonstrated efficient use of AI tools in development\n\n - Has developed in React.js applications\n\n - Has developed React Native applications for both IOS and Android\n\n - Display significant experience designing, debugging, and optimizing front-end applications to ensure speed and reliability\n\n - Thoroughly understand REST APIs and possess a strong grasp of HTTP requests\n\n - Understands test driven software development process (e.g. unit test)\n\n - Attention to pixel level design details\n\n - Proficient understanding of code versioning tools such as Git\n\n - Experience scaling front end engineering through component driven development - delivering re-usable modules and efficient web applications\n\nResponsibilities\n\n - Build features on responsive web and native applications\n\n - Leverage AI tools into their workflow to maintain efficiency\n\n - Fix bugs and issues that comes up\n\n - Work and collaborate with product and design teams\n\n - Attend all required project meetings\n\nSelection Process\n\n - Recruiter Screen\n\n - Live Coding Interview\n\n - Client Screening Interview\n\n - Client Technical Interview",
